msgctxt "0001"
msgid "I'm in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "How's it work again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid "I don't think so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid "...10 rupees."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid "50 rupees."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid "100 rupees!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid "I changed my mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Near00"
msgid "Place your bets!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid "<1.so>Psst... C'mere.<2.pa> No, closer."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey, hey, simmer down.<2.pa> I'm not talking\n"
"about anything illegal here."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: raw
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>See those treasure chests over there?<2.pa>\n"
"Whaddaya say to a little wager on 'em?<3.ra>The idea is you pick any "
"chest you want\n"
"and open it.<4.pa> Simple, right?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: raw
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"The best part is<1.pa> whatever chest you\n"
"open,<2.pa> you get all the money inside.<3.ra>Course, only one chest is "
"worth opening,\n"
"heh heh.<4.pa> Don't come crying to me if you\n"
"pick wrong."
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"Before you go opening any boxes,<1.pa> you'll\n"
"have to show me what it's worth to you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>What's a bet, after all, if you don't stand\n"
"to lose a bundle on it?<2.pa> That's the part\n"
"that really gets a man's heart racing!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It's up to you how much you want to\n"
"throw in.<2.pa> But the more you bet, the more\n"
"you stand to win.\n"
"A man like you must have expenses.<3.pa>\n"
"Couldn't hurt to make some quick cash—\n"
"right here, right now—<4.pa>am I right?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Whaddaya say?<2.pa> All you've got to lose\n"
"is your pride...and your money.<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "talk11"
msgid "<1.so>How 'bout it?<2.pa> Wanna try your luck?<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk12"
msgid "<1.so>All right, listen up."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Psh... <2.pa>Lady Luck has no time for a man\n"
"who won't take any chances."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Well, suit yourself.<2.pa> But if you ever feel\n"
"like trying your luck, I'm always here."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk15"
msgid "<1.so>Attaboy..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (long)
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "talk16"
msgid ""
"Now for the million-rupee question:<1.pa>\n"
"How much are you betting?<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk17"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Just tipping a toe in the water, eh?<2.pa>\n"
"Probably smart."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk18"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Now we're talkin'!<2.pa> Looks like someone's\n"
"ready to make some REAL money!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk19"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Way to live on the edge, pal!<2.pa> That\n"
"recklessness—I mean, fearlessness—\n"
"almost reminds me of me!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk20"
msgid ""
"<1.so>...Waaaait a minute.<2.pa> No making bets you\n"
"can't cover."
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk21"
msgid ""
"You can't gamble without putting cash on\n"
"the table.<1.pa> Come back when you have at\n"
"least enough to go for the minimum."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: raw
#. 4: pause (long)
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk22"
msgid ""
"<1.so>There we go.<2.pa> Step right up and take\n"
"your chances!<3.ra>Take all the time you need to choose a\n"
"chest to open.<4.pa> Look, listen, smell...<5.pa>taste\n"
"'em if you think it'll help."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk23"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Them's the breaks.<2.pa> But hey, surely you'll\n"
"win big NEXT time!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk24"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Whoa!<2.pa> Who'd have thought?!<3.pa> I mean,\n"
"it was pure luck, but..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk25"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Nice find!<2.pa> See what comes to those who\n"
"bet big?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk26"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Where did that...<2.pa> What did you...<3.pa> How\n"
"did you score a prize like that?!<4.pa> Can you\n"
"introduce me to Lady Luck?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "talk27"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You are gonna keep going, right?<2.pa> Or do\n"
"you admit defeat?<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk28"
msgid "<1.so>I hear you.<2.pa> Hey, if that's what you want..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk29"
msgid ""
"<1.so>What's with that look?<2.pa> Pay attention,\n"
"or Lady Luck will lose interest."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "talk30"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You must be feeling cocky if you're\n"
"talking to me instead of picking a chest.<2.ra>Just so you know, I don't "
"give do-overs.\n"
"You pay your money, and you take your\n"
"chances."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: raw
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: raw
#. 6: pause (short)
#. 7: sound
msgctxt "talk31"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You can only see inside the chest with\n"
"your heart, not your eyes.<2.ra>Close your eyes...<3.pa>look deep "
"inside...<4.pa>\n"
"and pray to Lady Luck...<5.ra>If you're truly sincere, she'll give you\n"
"the sign you—<6.pa> HAAAAhahahaha! I can't\n"
"finish with a straight face.\n"
"<7.so>What a load of hooey!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk32"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey, pal! Where're you going?<2.pa> There's\n"
"no chests outside. I wouldn't pull a fast\n"
"one on you like that.\n"
"<3.so>The prize is in one of these three chests,\n"
"cross my heart.<4.pa> Now get back here."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk33"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'll go get set up.<2.pa> No peeking while I'm\n"
"fiddling with the chests,<3.pa> got it?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk34"
msgid ""
"How'd you like to be rich...<1.pa>without\n"
"having to work for it?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: raw
#. 4: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk35"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Fair enough.<2.pa> Every good gambler knows\n"
"there's a time to walk away.<3.ra>I'm always here<4.pa> in case you ever "
"feel like\n"
"trying your luck again."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: raw
msgctxt "talk36"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Whoa there, buddy!<2.pa> Those aren't your\n"
"chests to open!<3.ra>But if you really wanna open them, have\n"
"I got a deal for you..."
msgstr ""

